LOOP FOREACH CurrentItem IN Files

    WAIT 3
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({F})Consolidated statement of comprehensive income for the year ended 31 December %Year%''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    WAIT 5
    UIAutomation.ExtractDataFromWindow.ExtractData Control: appmask['Pane \'Find in page 2021_Q1_PCH_Quarterly-Report_L.pdf\'']['Status Bar \'Result 1 of 1\''] BringToFront: True ExtractedData=> DataFromWindow
    Text.CropText.CropTextAfterFlag Text: DataFromWindow FromFlag: $'''of ''' IgnoreCase: True CroppedText=> CroppedText IsFlagFound=> IsFlagFound
    Text.ToNumber Text: CroppedText Number=> TextAsNumber
    SET DoubleOccurence TO 0
    LOOP LoopIndex FROM 1 TO TextAsNumber STEP 1
        UIAutomation.ExtractDataFromWindow.ExtractData Control: appmask['Pane \'Find in page 2021_Q1_PCH_Quarterly-Report_L.pdf\'']['Edit \'Page number\''] BringToFront: True ExtractedData=> DataFromWindow2
        IF DataFromWindow2 <> DoubleOccurence THEN
            Pdf.ExtractTablesFromPDF.ExtractTablesFromPage PDFFile: CurrentItem.FullName PageNumber: DataFromWindow2 MultiPageTables: True SetFirstRowAsHeader: False ExtractedPDFTables=> ExtractedPDFTables
            IF IsNotEmpty(ExtractedPDFTables) THEN
                Excel.AddWorksheet Instance: ExcelInstance Name: $'''%Year%_%LoopIndex%''' WorksheetPosition: Excel.WorksheetPosition.Last
                Excel.WriteToExcel.Write Instance: ExcelInstance Value: ExtractedPDFTables[0].Datatable
                Pdf.ExtractPages PDFFile: CurrentItem.FullName PageSelection: DataFromWindow2 ExtractedPDFPath: $'''%ExtractedPDFFolder%\\%CurrentItem.NameWithoutExtension%_Intermediate.pdf''' IfFileExists: Pdf.IfFileExists.Overwrite ExtractedPDFFile=> ExtractedPDF
                SET DoubleOccurence TO DataFromWindow2
            END
        END
        MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Return}''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: True
    END
    MouseAndKeyboard.SendKeys.FocusAndSendKeys TextToSend: $'''{Control}({F4})''' DelayBetweenKeystrokes: 10 SendTextAsHardwareKeys: False
END
